Welcome! How are you finding
Luxuria? Chilly, isn't it?

rows.label: tlk44500183_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I recommend the Steamed
Veg Stralu. It'll warm
you up from head to toe!

rows.label: tlk44500183_01_msg0005

Nice of you to drop by, Owner! Still
a bit nippy, isn't it? What you need
is a generous helping of Stralu!
